'''Perivi John Katjavivi''', ni  umukinnyi wa firime [[Ubwongereza|w'Abongereza]] na [[namibiya]] .   Yakinnye filime nyinshi   harimo ''Eembwiti,'' unseen na ''Film Festival Film.'' Usibye gutanga icyerekezo, ni numuproducer, umwanditsi, ukora kamera, umukinnyi, cinematografi akaba n'umwanditsi. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Katjavivi yavukiye Oxford mu Bwongereza kandi afite barumuna be batanu. Se Peter Katjavivi ni umunyapolitiki n'umudipolomate wa [[Namibiya]], currently  umuvugizi w'Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Namibiya, nyina ni [[Umwongereza]] Jane Katjavivi. 

== Umwuga ==
Muri 2016, Katjavivi yakoze filime ye yambere  ''The Unseen'' . Iyi filime yerekanwe mu birori byinshi bya firime harimo na Busan, mu marushanwa yabereye i Durban. Filime yatsindiye igihembo cya Filime Nziza muri Innsbruck no muri [[Otirishiya]].  Muri 2019, yakoze ''Filime ngufi ya Film Festival'', afatanya na Mpumelelo Mcata. Filime ifite Premiere yisi kuri 69 ya Berlinale muri Gashyantare 2019. 

Usibye sinema, yanditse kandi byinshi kuri ''Windhoek Indorerezi'', ''Afurika ni Igihugu'' na ''OkayAfrica'' . 

